query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('accelerometer',
'android-preferences',
'fosuserbundle',
'monodevelop',
'rack',
'rdbms',
'sdl-2',
'trim',
'windows-server-2008',
'xib');
